channel.title: Game crashes after rocket engine
channel.description:
As the topic says the game crashes for me when going down the hole after the three-headed monster gets killed by the rocket engine.
I don't know how to get past this part. Half way down the hole the game is loading the next area, but it crashes instead. Really annoying.
I would really appreciate some help.
